      <p class="season-body">We walk through late-season hedgerow and woodland, harvesting elderberries, rosehips, hawthorn berries, and sloe. We look at the immune-modulating herbs — echinacea, astragalus, elderberry — and understand the difference between stimulating and modulating immunity (a difference that matters enormously for people with autoimmune or inflammatory conditions).</p>
